Normal
When an opponent's monster declares an attack: Change all monsters you control to Defense Position, also for the rest of this turn, when a face-up "Performapal" monster(s) you control is destroyed by battle or card effect, return that monster(s) to the hand instead of sending it to the Graveyard.
